    <specific name="Magic Item Type"> Ring </specific>
    <specific name="Tier"/>
    <specific name="_Item_Set_ID"/>
    <specific name="Armor"/>
    <specific name="Weapon"/>
    <specific name="Item Slot"> Ring </specific>
    <specific name="Requirement"/>
    <specific name="Critical"/>
    <specific name="Special"/>
    <specific name="Power"> Power (Daily * Radiant): Immediate Reaction. You may use this ability after you have been damaged by a melee attack. All creatures within 5 squares of you who have dealt damage to you during this encounter are dealt 3d10 radiant damage.
