Power (Daily): Immediate reaction. Use after being struck by a marked creature. This attack does not count. Re-roll the attack roll.

Power (Daily): Free action. Use after making a successful attack against a marked creature. Your attack deals an additional 1W and the creature is dazed until the end of its next turn. </specific>
